dc:description: Miniature Jar. Pale green glass. Intact. Lots of golden iridescence. Material good. Some small bubbles. Black impurities. Toilet bottle. Rim outsplayed horizontally and turned down slightly. Short cylindrical neck. Sloping shoulder. Body cylindrical, with shoulder and base slightly wider. Concave base with kick and pontil mark.
Gazda: Toilet bottle. Glass, free blown.
